  "text": "Type of substance use disorder was assessed by using the Composite International Diagnostic Interview, Substance Abuse Module (CIDI-SAM) [CITATION_1] . The CIDI-SAM is an expanded and more detailed version of the substance use sections of the CIDI. The interview questions address the diagnostic criteria of DSM-IV-TR and ICD-10 psychoactive SUD.",
